  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">We may also use pixel tags which are small graphic files that allow us to monitor the use of the Services A pixel tag can collect information such as the IP address of the computer that downloaded the page on which the tag appears the URL of the page on which the pixel tag appears the time and length of time the page containing the pixel tag was viewed the type of browser that retrieved the pixel tag and the identification number of any cookie previously placed by that server on your computer</evidence>
